.	operating choices for utility i in iserver1.msm
.
__I_FLOAT	$equ	1	. 1 = do integer 72-bit [ multiply divide ] in floating point
				. for 72-bit multiplier / divisor / remainder

__IM_INLINE1	$equ	0	. 1 = if not __I_FLOAT do integer 72-bit multiply
				. per macro ../lib/i72.def:i72m, otherwise with inline code

__ID_INLINE1	$equ	0	. 1 = if not __I_FLOAT do integer 72-bit divide
				. per macro ../lib/i72.def:i72d, otherwise with inline code

__I_DMAGNITUDE	$equ	0	. 1 = override other divide options
				. do a cautious 3-stage divide on positive magnitude values
